{"type": "article", "id": 21219, "title": "城市建筑戒指", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-25T07:30:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021300024xWTnSDrdNLAvm9C.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t俄罗斯的设计师 Ola Shekhtman 将建筑融入到戒指里，每一组戒指都有一个城市的地标式建筑，一共选择了纽约、旧金山、巴黎、香港、阿姆斯特丹等 12 个城市。比如代表巴黎的戒指上有凯旋门、带有玻璃金字塔门的卢浮宫、埃菲尔铁塔、风车等元素，转到不同的角度可以看到不同的建筑，很精巧，也有点哥特风。材料上可以选择铂金、银、铜等定制，适合送礼物。<a href=\"http://www.etsy.com/shop/Shekhtwoman?ref=shopsection_shophome_leftnav&amp;source=aw&amp;awc=6220_1453639139_a5742bd0f74b584249bef51753d81929&amp;utm_source=affiliate_window&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=us_location_buyer&amp;utm_content=102463\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150832lZrQbVox4kYDMzRt.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150833MUfPLptmKgj6yRT9.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150833MK7Ncn2mo5B43bOl.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150834Slu6FfGWVTAjrRJb.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261508347Lb1sivPXIgomBh6.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}